  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0dc3\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca 28000\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d87\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "28000 tourists came in July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Tourism Development Authority, 28 733 tourists have come to Sri Lanka in the first 19 days of July. Along with that number, the number of tourists who have come to Sri Lanka so far this year is 440110, said the authority.",
        "England, India and Germany have become the three countries where the largest number of tourists have visited Sri Lanka this month.",
        "However, since the state of emergency is currently in force in the country, this will cause some hindrance to tourist arrivals in the future, according to representatives of the tourism industry."
      ],
